{"tid":1663094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[NBA戰線]Irving 出聲講中港問題！","createTime":"2019-10-19T07:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T14:38:57.000Z","uid":72962,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"600aace4aba7dcc01e3ca65eb58b16454539dcfe","tid":1663094,"uid":72962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:55:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/malika_andrews/status/1185385477098164226?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmalika_andrews%2Fstatus%2F1185385477098164226%3Fs%3D21&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=96f90b0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmalika_andrews%2Fstatus%2F1185385477098164226%3Fs%3D21&h=9d2ed240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/malika_andrews/status/1185385477098164226?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sportsyeah.hk/2019/10/19/%e5%8d%a1%e7%88%be%e8%89%be%e6%a6%ae%e7%82%ba%e6%b8%af%e7%99%bc%e8%81%b2%ef%bc%9a%e9%bb%91%e4%ba%ba%e5%92%8c%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e5%90%8c%e6%a8%a3%e5%8f%97%e5%bc%b7%e6%ac%8a%e5%a3%93%e8%bf%ab/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsportsyeah.hk%2F2019%2F10%2F19%2F%25e5%258d%25a1%25e7%2588%25be%25e8%2589%25be%25e6%25a6%25ae%25e7%2582%25ba%25e6%25b8%25af%25e7%2599%25bc%25e8%2581%25b2%25ef%25bc%259a%25e9%25bb%2591%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%2592%258c%25e6%25b8%25af%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%2590%258c%25e6%25a8%25a3%25e5%258f%2597%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e6%25ac%258a%25e5%25a3%2593%25e8%25bf%25ab%2F&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=b0682525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sportsyeah.hk/2019/10/19/%e5%8d%a1%e7%88%be%e8%89%be%e6%a6%ae%e7%82%ba%e6%b8%af%e7%99%bc%e8%81%b2%ef%bc%9a%e9%bb%91%e4%ba%ba%e5%92%8c%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e5%90%8c%e6%a8%a3%e5%8f%97%e5%bc%b7%e6%ac%8a%e5%a3%93%e8%bf%ab/</a><br />\n<br />\nSportsyeah 報道<br />\n<br />\n勒邦占士（LeBron James）和中共官方聲言應處分發帖支持香港反修例抗爭的火箭總經理莫雷（Daryl Morey），卻照樣有人選擇唱反調。效力布魯克林籃網的卡爾艾榮（Kyrie Irving）表達他對港人的支持。艾榮在日前出席對多倫多速龍的季前熱身賽時，表示為個人信念發聲是天職。<br />\n<br />\n雖然籃網班主蔡崇信公開譴責莫雷的言論，是鼓吹分裂中國、支持港獨，但艾榮照樣不理，說：「作為一個人，我們應該堅守自己的信念。我知道香港、中國之間正處理一些問題。即便在美國，有色人種日日都遭受壓迫，仍有不少人為自由付出，這也我聯想到香港的情況。作為身處美國的黑人，去談及這些問題時會發現當中有共通處，特別因為這些事都是影響自由以及世界和平。」<br />\n<br />\nESPN更指，艾榮在上海出席NBA主席阿當蕭華（Adam Silver）召開的湖人、籃網球員會議時，表達四個主張：內在的平靜、自由、平等，以及世界和平，一旦事態的發展與上述主張有矛盾的話，他必定發聲。艾榮更謂，如果兩隊比賽的同時要為莫雷事件善後，不打也罷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人同美國黑人connect!<br />\n大家快twitter <br />\n可以用hashtag #thankyouIrving"},{"pid":"f425263fa4d578f25cba066f2c150b5d2d27045f","tid":1663094,"uid":72962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:57:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec4499bf9cedcaed973cbdf365461f73a0aaad3e","tid":1663094,"uid":10014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:58:21.000Z","msg":"嘩 咁佢會唔會就咁坐bench？"},{"pid":"fb666c90f27eaead08d6ac19db380954847cca83","tid":1663094,"uid":294614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/XcwJ1iz.gif\" />"},{"pid":"9e7e8bd909fa29d2dc323e75dc4c2c4e1843cbec","tid":1663094,"uid":283908,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:58:58.000Z","msg":"同班主唱反調"},{"pid":"5efe7c72bc476724cbef91245adf77aa6a0926c0","tid":1663094,"uid":64636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:59:01.000Z","msg":"佢同james真係好fd <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee7462bb5a51070b774629eb48726ed0019f837","tid":1663094,"uid":69872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:59:30.000Z","msg":"其實佢講完好似冇咁講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfaba14d5f40d7f0c5d8c9d55aab4c0c5fb172b","tid":1663094,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:59:30.000Z","msg":"提大家今日有咩活動 10 &middot; 