:1663094,"uid":177590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec4499bf9cedcaed973cbdf365461f73a0aaad3e","tid":1663094,"uid":10014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:58:21.000Z","msg":"嘩 咁佢會唔會就咁坐bench？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:28:00.000Z","msg":"籃網想輸咪叫佢坐BENCH囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2365460d3a63507a2ab2205fb1c7849b4983fe","tid":1663094,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:29:11.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"1b7b43d184d98f1b5c7bab5a39192b2e40a29ffb","tid":1663094,"uid":69872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9be2425b7b27bbeb8d46afddb6692393792b51a","tid":1663094,"uid":177590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec4499bf9cedcaed973cbdf365461f73a0aaad3e","tid":1663094,"uid":10014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T07:58:21.000Z","msg":"嘩 咁佢會唔會就咁坐bench？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T08:28:00.000Z","msg":"籃網想輸咪叫佢坐BENCH囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T10:22:29.000Z","msg":"冇可能 發表意見就bench 係美國冇可能發生 <br />\n<br />\n唔係完全大是大非（種族，殺人）<br />\n<br />\n美國係完全支持言論自由 你可以屌9返佢，但唔可以做出d咩封殺行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"568de440395323f00621ed012fc4acf8e24ccd61","tid":1663094,"uid":233193,"li